      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just more noise. \"meaningful impact\" is just a cope people use to ignore the fact that the math doesn't add up. eventually the sun burns out, the stars go dark, and nothing we do actually matters. if nothing matters, then why keep participating in the struggle? why keep pushing through the boredom and the pain just to reach the same inevitable nothingness?",
